OL,3,CHitler and Nazis fanatic given
OL,4,Csuspended sentence
OL,6,FA man who posted support online for
OL,7,FAdolf Hitler and the Nazis has been
OL,8,Fgiven a suspended sentence.
OL,10,FHarris Girling, 57, posted more than
OL,11,F4,000 times between August 2021 and
OL,12,Fhis arrest in February 2023, with the
OL,13,Foverall theme embracing Nazi ideology
OL,14,Fand hatred of Jews.
OL,16,FHis online posts included hatred
OL,17,Fagainst Muslims, black people, Jews
OL,18,Fand gay people.
