OL,6,FPreston Crown Court heard how, at an
OL,7,Fearlier hearing, Girling, from Nelson,
OL,8,FLancashire, who had no previous
OL,9,Fconvictions, admitted eight counts of
OL,10,Fstirring hatred online mostly of
OL,11,Fracial hatred but also based on sexual
OL,12,Forientation.
OL,14,FWhen police seized his devices, they
OL,15,Fincluded images of Adolf Hitler.
OL,17,FGirling used the US-based social media
OL,18,Fplatform Gab, using a public profile
OL,19,Fso anyone could see his hateful
OL,20,Fmessages.
