OL,6,FJoe Allman, prosecuting, told the
OL,7,Fcourt Girling's posts online received
OL,8,Fvery few responses and this could not
OL,9,Fbe regarded as widespread
OL,10,Fdissemination of hate speech.
OL,12,FBrendan O'Leary, mitigating, said the
OL,13,Fdefendant, a father-of-one, whose wife
OL,14,Flives in Romania, had worked as a
OL,15,Fpsychiatric nurse and had in the past
OL,16,Fbeen a supporter of left-wing,
OL,17,Fprogressive politics.
