OL,6,FMr O'Leary continued: "What appears to
OL,7,Fhave happened is in 2020 and
OL,8,Fthereafter, in deteriorating health,
OL,9,Fsignificant medication, his
OL,10,Fpredilection towards isolation
OL,11,Fcompounded by lockdown, ill health led
OL,12,Fhim down a path that's quite frankly
OL,13,Fhard to explain.
OL,15,F"He appears to be someone in the midst
OL,16,Fof very difficult personal
OL,17,Fcircumstances, he's sought an avenue
OL,18,Fto express his frustration, wholly
OL,19,Finappropriately."
