OL,11,Fmonths in prison on each count, but
OL,12,Fsuspended for 20 months, with 35
OL,13,Frehabilitation days and a 26-week
OL,14,Fcurfew.
OL,16,FHe said: "The decision to suspend has
OL,17,Fbeen a very finely balanced one.
